history.content:
Hello,

I am interested in taking an Info class to fulfill a technical course, and I noticed that some Info classes show up on this list:

https://eecs.berkeley.edu/resources/undergrads/cs/degree-reqs/tech-electives

But they do not show up on this list (in the technical list box):

http://guide.berkeley.edu/undergraduate/degree-programs/computer-science/#majorrequirementstext

For example, one such class is Info 253A

How should I interpret this?

(Thank you in advance)
history.subject: Technical Class Confusion
